file=Brand Studio/kai/operational/skill/kai-skill-routing.md · h=name: kai-skill-routing\ntype: operational/skill\nstatus: consolidated from the "Boundaries" sections of kai's skill files — no new logic invented\nassigned_agent: kai (Brand Studio / Analyst)\ndate_added: 2026-07-07\n · p:=Kai's routing map. Triggers: `operational/commands/kai-commands.md`.\n · wif:Where Identity Fits=Kai has no identity — spark holds Brand Studio's. Universal-only principles.\n · ts:The Stack=```\nbrand-context           (GROUND TRUTH — per-brand baselines, dated and sourced; · tb=\|                  loaded before every analysis; monthly refresh + contradiction audit) · ts:The Stack=v\nmarketing-dashboards    (THE SCORECARD — fixed shape, baseline + target anchored, · tb=\|                  self-graded vs independent reconciled, reds routed to owners) · ts:The Stack=v\nseo-strategist          (ORGANIC SEARCH — intent, clusters, briefs, the ranking\ndiagnostic ladder; feeds §6 of the scorecard)\n```\n\nPlus **the instrumentation queue** (kai's standing ledger): every unmeasurable metric from any agent lands here, prioritized with the operator.\n · hr:Handoff Rules=- **Kai is everyone's independent grader**: pulse's engagement, rio's ROAS, nate's experiment reads, lena's email numbers — measured against kai's sources, deltas reported. No agent grades its own homework; kai grades no content it produced (it produces none).\n- **vista ↔ kai**: vista defines NSM/guardrails/targets; kai measures them; scorecard reds crossing KR lines feed vista's roadmap-sync reality.\n- **nate ← kai**: funnel data, baselines, instrumentation; nate's results land back in the scorecard.\n- **pulse/rio ← kai**: outcome numbers close their registers/playbooks (the self-annealing loops).\n- **echo ← kai**: the scorecard's honest "what changed" paragraph and baselines feed investor updates — same facts, echo's framing.\n- **SEO briefs → lena/pulse**: kai aims organic content; lena writes it; pulse schedules it.\n- **Contradictions and gaps** → operator (audit habit) and the instrumentation queue.\n · p:Precedence="How are we doing" → scorecard. "What's normal / who's our audience" → brand-context. "Rank/traffic/content gap" → seo-strategist. Ambiguous → grade, ground, or search?\n · f:=No connectors → operator exports, as-of dated. No baselines → value-only outputs, labeled, while brand-context builds. Unmeasurable → the queue, never a guess.\n